# Ski-Jahorina

Android app for Jahorina resort. Package: `com.neoapps.skijahorina`.

## Stack
- Kotlin, minSdk 30, compileSdk 35
- Navigation Component + Fragments (hub: `SkiCenterDetailsFragment`)
- ViewModels, Kotpref, Retrofit/OkHttp to shared Railway API
- AdMob interstitials via `RotatingInterstitialAdManager`

## Layout
- `features/skicenter/` - hub, lifts, weather, cameras, map, apartments, useful info
- `common/` - prefs, icons, binders
- `common/ads/` - remote ads config fetch/cache + screen IDs

## Backend
- Shared `ski-serbia-api` on Railway
- Resort data + `GET /v1/ads-config/ski_jahorina`
- API key from `local.properties` / BuildConfig - never commit secrets

## Workflow
- Match existing UI/patterns; prefer small focused diffs
- Commit only when asked
- Remote ads: DB controls `enabled` / `every_n_clicks` for screens already wired in `AdsScreens`
